{"tid":658513,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"因為復仇者聯盟，搞到我俾人打到入廠...","createTime":"2018-05-09T05:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T13:55:11.000Z","uid":125434,"like":17,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"94f6aca8bdcf5832f8ccb385e37a3c32627ef8f7","tid":658513,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"屌，就話說頭先同女朋友去深水埗嗰頭食嘢，途中經過一間賣碟舖，就播緊復仇者聯盟唔知第幾集，我條女唔係好識入面啲角色，淨係認得變形俠醫但係又up唔出個名，一尾喺度講：「史力加呀！史力加出場啦！」咁我咪笑佢on9，我話：「乜撚嘢史力加呀？邊撚個史力加呀？」<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候就有三個黑鬼經過，特登停喺度啤住我，仲要行埋黎都唔知搞乜撚...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑鬼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : Hey<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : Hey dude? What can I help you bro?<br />\n<br />\n我以為佢想問路啦，我屌點知佢無啦啦轉用廣東話同我講:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你啱啱係咪話我地係死nigga? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 吓...唔係呀...我話「史力加」呀...<br />\n<br />\n之後班黑鬼圍埋喺度唔知講乜撚，我同條女英文差淨係聽到個gym字，今次仆街啦，佢哋係咪想話搵個最大隻有做gym嘅嚟打柒我？聽到個gym字，我第一時間諗起自己都讀過黑人民權運動馬丁路德金，於是我就想大叫句金句出嚟表示友好：但由於嗰陣太過緊張，我完全表達唔到...將I have a dream ! fight for black people ! freedom! 講咗做:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : I have gym! fight ! fight black people ! three ! three ! <br />\n<br />\n就係咁嗰三個nigga以為我係想撩佢地隻揪，最後俾人打到我爆曬肛，依加去緊醫院。屌你老母復仇者聯盟真係害死我，出新一集都唔撚會睇..."},{"pid":"3d745bc626a4e5eeeaf8743cdc6bd7964f021911","tid":658513,"uid":7915,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:06:50.000Z","msg":"劇情欠缺張力"},{"pid":"72d73b8efe81c01f5e2148627cf5d29400e9833c","tid":658513,"uid":6248,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"9f6fec58021f44836dda0e95f2a8b190c72335d2","tid":658513,"uid":119688,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"重作啦柒頭"},{"pid":"079d2c76a74e8fbff75a1583cf29471a94e0a5a6","tid":658513,"uid":176802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"on9當有趣"},{"pid":"0eb7e3bbd9a2f0d5ab2f102941bf2c9d0beeca34","tid":658513,"uid":18241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"你講 哇卡打科eva 就無事啦.."},{"pid":"10b156a0323356489a3ac58c28d6bc0c1c45db48","tid":658513,"uid":19499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的呢？"},{"pid":"281fc7605322a152e592b32ef21f9fbc8cfe65e4","tid":658513,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"f7dcac41a186751ed55e4395ec71bf4fc344ba66","tid":658513,"uid":101328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536086fe3b4de892144863bb1c6e6ecf6d15816b","tid":658513,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 咩喵 )"},{"pid":"e17b0306b838fe289cfa849cbe35eba69d46b093","tid":658513,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb952117738b4a4e15ec72b214963b7218f86f9c","tid":658513,"uid":54720,"li